{"tid":1443861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"既然香港班狗對大陸佬視而不見","createTime":"2019-08-11T10:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:12:54.000Z","uid":223300,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4041e46ebd728a41c8bd0d28fe55ffb945a9d2da","tid":1443861,"uid":223300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"咁我地都可以將計就計，手執中國國旗，繼續示威，發表五大訴求，一來仆街林奠冇得轉移視線話我地港獨，二來中國狗、中聯扮話唔到你外國勢力、別有用心，而只係一班&ldquo;愛國&rdquo;既香港人爭取權利。有冇得諗?"},{"pid":"43007e721a9dbec834728e2e5265d46c72daf298","tid":1443861,"uid":109820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"有得諗 但做之前要拎大部分共識<br />\n所以幫你輕輕一推先<br />\n<br />\n【小心中計】如果我係敵人，我會想<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dAzCJS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dAzCJS</a>"},{"pid":"25b95b903c12b7acdf7e3c91b64e369389f3a06e","tid":1443861,"uid":223300,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"講真，我地又唔係要港獨，只係要林奠回應五大訴求，我地打正中國人既旗號去爭取呢樣野，中共又可能唔會干涉，林奠條仆街又冇藉口將港獨亂咁套落我地身上，佢仲有咩牌可以出?<br />\n隨時有真大陸佬黎支持我地添，咁又唔洗搞到左右受敵，到時可以專心槍頭對準個仆街港共政權!"},{"pid":"6b19b9539042b602e8dcb256ebf7de71c28d867f","tid":1443861,"uid":223300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:42:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26d48348663295ca8aaf67bdf09f3e9f0f73c16f","tid":1443861,"uid":223300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a2b2ca81e6d105df66e51e34d992610e795481d6","tid":1443861,"uid":223300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:42:57.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"9a1ce27c24266c39fdbd6e5ff4fbe9786a4e9c4a","tid":1443861,"uid":223300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"947541aa2657673976e7ee07459279796cce1f6e","tid":1443861,"uid":223300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"f